# Interpreter for 'vpn-switch openvpn add <group>' command
# Terminal function (_openvpn_add1) that creates group directories
#
# Default value: "sh"
#   Executes shell commands output by _openvpn_add1
#
# Function behavior:
#   Creates group directory: mkdir -p "$VPN_SWITCH_BASE/openvpn/$group"
#   Sets permissions: chmod 0700 "$VPN_SWITCH_BASE/openvpn/$group"
#
# This is part of a HETEROGENEOUS family (mixed terminal/combinator functions).
# See VPN_SWITCH_INTERPRETER_wireguard_add for family-level documentation pattern.
